ow it is viewed in the context of one vast unitary evolving entity of which we are \"bits\" + as bits we speed up just as it speeds up - or does it speed up? Isn't it in itself qua MMSK. actually already perfectly + completely there? It is we who evolve along the change-rate velocity axis, from slow to fast, \"center to rim,\" as it were 194 So my personal evolution moves me alon an axis that we call \"linear time + this is somewhat correct but only superficially So, because this \"time\" axis is really an axis of proportional velocity of change-rate freedom, complexity of organization, abstractness + consciousness (+ I suppose a lot else, like individuality + uniqueness, spirituality, kind ness, etc), + so indeed our temporal \"sets are literally coaxial, because the whole thing is organized conceptually - the MMSK. Now, I view this as an entelechy with all of us as bits within it + in a real sense micro-par its of it. + we traverse it calong the axis I describe above). Let me say, that meta‐ abstraction qua insight was of an unprece dented magnitude + could, then, conceivably have generated a leap during my life time along the above-depicted axis, like (als ob) instant Karma (rather than reward after death in the next world or next life). Revealing the nature of the situation would not be a matter taken into consideration (i.e. \"Phil Dick now knows the truth, that we are dead + in the triune afterlife\" etc) because there is no min D or being decreeing my advance up the axis; It's all governed - as Spinoza taught - by natural law; viz: if you have an insight of that magnitude you will leap up the axis de facto due to the nature of the total entity + what your own nature con sists of, + no eschatological judge need be involved it's as natural as weighing fruit on a scale: the heavier the fruit the lower the Scah Platform will dro (195 Now, I was lying there last night going to sleep + I realized that my 2-74 meta-abstraction was (astonishingly) a realization that 